INHLANGANO yokhetho kuleli i-IEC ithi iyasithokozela isinqumo seNkantolo yezoKhetho sokuhlehlisa izinhlelo zokhetho lokuchibiyela obekufanele lubanjwe ezindaweni ezahlukene. I-IEC ithumele isitatimende sabezindaba ngoLwesibili ichaza ukuthi ukubheduka kwegciwane iCorona (Covid-19) kwenze kwaphoqeleka ukuba kuhlehle izinhlelo zokhetho. Isitatimende sithi inkantolo ikhombe uJuni 3 no-10 njengezinsuku okungase kuqhutshekwe ngazo nezinhlelo zokhetho. Kuvela nokuthi ukhetho bekufanele lubanjwe ezinsukwini ezingu-90 lapho kuvalwa khona izikhala zamakhansela kodwa akuvumelekile ukuthi lubanjwe emuva kwezinsuku ezingu-120, emuva kokuphuma kwesinqumo senkantolo. Ngenxa yale micilikishi kuzophoqeleka ukuthi ikhalenda lokhetho libuyekezwe kabusha ukuze kuqondanisiwe kahle konke. Inkantolo iphinde yanika i-IEC igunya lokuthi ibuyele kuyo izofaka isicelo sokuhlehlisa uma kunesidingo. Izifundazwe ebezilinde ukuba nokhetho komasipala bazo yi-Eastern Cape , North West , KwaZulu-Natal ,Gauteng naseWestern Cape. E-Eastern Cape bekuzokhethwa kuMasipala iWalter Sisulu , uMzimvubu ne-Amahahlathi.Â  INorth West ibizoba nokhetho komasipala iRusternburg neJB Marks. KwaZulu-Natal bekuzokhethwa koMasipala oPhongolo naseRay Nkonyeni kanti eWestern Cape bekuzoba eDrankenstein 